* Title
  SWatantra ARM or SWARM for in short
* Objectives
  - to compile Linux kernel images for any ARM device that you could lay hands on
  - to create a generic rootFS (root filesystem) 
  - to create customized root file systems for specific domains, such
    as school education, OLPC, college students, developers, mobility,
    research etc.

  
